OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778868675
OL,3,CMan guilty of attempting to murder
OL,4,Cpolice officers in Strabane
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fattempting to murder police officers
OL,8,Fin a New IRA bomb attack in Strabane
OL,9,Fin 2022.
OL,11,FCharlie Love, 31 from Bridge Street in
OL,12,FStrabane was convicted on four charges
OL,13,Fat Belfast Crown Court on Thursday.
OL,15,FMr Justice Fowler said he was
OL,16,Fsatisfied Love was "intimately
OL,17,Fconnected with the planning and
OL,18,Fexecution of what was a dissident
OL,19,Fterrorist bomb attack on a police car
OL,20,Fwith two officers on board".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
