FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778868675
OL,3,CMan guilty of attempting to murder
OL,4,Cpolice officers in Strabane
OL,6,F"I am satisfied that it was the
OL,7,Fdefendant's intention that police
OL,8,Fofficers would be killed."
OL,10,FThe judge also rejected suggestions
OL,11,Fthe bomb attack was an "elaborate
OL,12,Fincident to scare or terrorise the
OL,13,Fpolice" and instead said it fell
OL,14,Fwithin a "violent dissident terrorism
OL,15,Fagenda."
OL,17,FThe four charges arose from an attack
OL,18,Fon a police vehicle in the Mount
OL,19,FCarmel Heights area of Strabane in
OL,20,FNovember 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778868675
OL,3,CMan guilty of attempting to murder
OL,4,Cpolice officers in Strabane
OL,6,FTwo officers were in an unmarked
OL,7,Farmoured Skoda Superb around 11pm when
OL,8,Fthey reported seeing a flash and
OL,9,Fhearing a "massive bang".
OL,11,FLove's DNA was located on a modified
OL,12,Fcordless drill and on a command wire
OL,13,Flocated at the site of the attack.
OL,15,FHe denied all the charges levelled at
OL,16,Fhim during the non-jury trial but was
OL,17,Ffound guilty on all four charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
