PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778868675
OL,3,CMan guilty of attempting to murder
OL,4,Cpolice officers in Strabane
OL,6,FThey were namely the attempted murder
OL,7,Fof 'Officer A' and 'Officer B',
OL,8,Fpossessing explosives and causing an
OL,9,Fexplosion likely to endanger life or
OL,10,Fcause serious injury to property.
OL,12,FHe will be sentenced in September.
